Author: chpbnvic
Text: I know right. I don’t go telling people I have an ED or I binge now but I totally feel like they’d be like “you? An ED? Uh isn’t that supposed to make you skinny?”. FML

Author: naturally_sourced
Text: Binger here too. It sucks so much, especially since you feel so out of control, and it's a cycle of eating (and eating and eating and eating) and hating yourself, then doing the exact same thing tomorrow. And then feeling invalid, because EDs are meant to make you skINnY right??? (at least according uninformed people)  I don't smoke (or juul) so won't put my 2 cents in. Just be careful! We do have a predisposition to get addicted easily.
